reviewText: My 4  year old granddaughter watches this over and over again.
These usually hold my kids attention for a while, this one didn't. It didn't seem as fun as the others.
My daughter and I are huge Cat n the Hat fans. These educational DVDs are the best that I'm collecting them all!!!

Martin Short is a TERRIFIC voice for this cartoon. My kids loooove learning about nature and science with these videos! It's educational and very humorous so even if mom & dad are in the room watching it's enjoyable (no offense Dora...okay a lot of offense, your voice is like nails on a chalkboard). This is an A+ purchase.

our grandson loved it!  He sits quietly watching.  We all learns something from these videos.

There is nothing violent in these.
